   BCA Collection Logo LABOR BOARD OF CONTRACT APPEALS
   The Contract Disputes Act of 1978, as amended, provides for the
   resolution of disputes arising under Federal procurement contracts and
   for the creation and functioning of Federal agency Boards of Contract
   Appeals.


